  "prompt": "What is the best Instagram followers tracking app?",
  "response": "There are several popular apps for tracking Instagram followers that can help you monitor your growth, engagement, and audience insights. Here are some of the best options available:\n\n1. **Iconosquare**: This is a comprehensive analytics tool that provides in-depth insights into your Instagram account, including follower growth, engagement rates, and post performance.\n\n2. **Hootsuite**: While primarily a social media management tool, Hootsuite offers analytics features that allow you to track your Instagram followers and engagement metrics.\n\n3. **Social Blade**: This is a web-based tool that provides analytics for various social media platforms, including Instagram. You can track follower counts and engagement rates over time.\n\n4. **Follower Analyzer for Instagram**: This app provides insights into your followers, including who unfollowed you, who your ghost followers are, and engagement metrics.\n\n5. **Analisa.io**: This tool offers detailed analytics for Instagram accounts and hashtags. You can track follower growth and engagement statistics.\n\n6. **Later**: Primarily a scheduling tool, Later also offers Instagram analytics features that help you understand your audience and track follower activity.\n\n7. **Insights (Instagram's native feature)**: Instagram itself offers insights for business accounts, providing data on follower demographics, engagement, and reach.\n\nWhen choosing an app, consider your specific needs, such as whether you want detailed analytics, the ability to schedule posts, or other features. Always ensure that the app you choose complies with Instagram's terms of service.",
